{"lang":"zh","stage":4,"title":"fuller short sentences","sentences":[{"t":"你知道那首歌吗？","en":"Do you know that song?","r":"Nǐ zhīdào nà shǒu gē ma?","a":"n_1835736f29b2.mp3"},{"t":"你当然可以。","en":"Of course you can.","r":"Nǐ dāngrán kěyǐ.","a":"n_e94023995923.mp3"},{"t":"门票多少钱？","en":"How much does it cost to get in?","r":"Ménpiào duōshao qián?","a":"n_71490e2176b7.mp3"},{"t":"我应该少工作点。","en":"I should work less.","r":"Wǒ yīnggāi shǎo gōngzuò diǎn.","a":"n_83ad447b570b.mp3"},{"t":"这个你应该知道。","en":"You should know this.","r":"Zhège nǐ yīnggāi zhīdào.","a":"n_c8ff5edcb18f.mp3"},{"t":"外面冷吗？","en":"Is it cold outside?","r":"Wàimiàn lěng ma?","a":"n_6c66cd896c86.mp3"},{"t":"我在写作业。","en":"I'm doing the homework.","r":"Wǒ zài xiě zuòyè.","a":"n_e2565700afe8.mp3"},{"t":"作业我写完了。","en":"I did my homework.","r":"Zuòyè wǒ xiě wán le.","a":"n_e7fcc632174c.mp3"},{"t":"别那么做。","en":"Don't do that.","r":"Bié nàme zuò.","a":"n_7cd962c14c43.mp3"},{"t":"跟我说实话。","en":"Tell me the truth.","r":"Gēn wǒ shuō shíhuà.","a":"n_197a9192e5ed.mp3"},{"t":"告诉我是谁。","en":"Tell me who it was.","r":"Gàosu wǒ shì shéi.","a":"n_ce5357295028.mp3"},{"t":"问她吧。","en":"Ask her.","r":"Wèn tā ba.","a":"n_a4a6257418c9.mp3"},{"t":"问他要多少。","en":"Ask him how much he wants.","r":"Wèn tā yào duōshao.","a":"n_c221397da776.mp3"},{"t":"我给你一个。","en":"I'll give you one.","r":"Wǒ gěi nǐ yí ge.","a":"n_97e2699742dd.mp3"},{"t":"我去哪儿找？","en":"Where do I look for it?","r":"Wǒ qù nǎr zhǎo?","a":"n_b6b0e6b64166.mp3"},{"t":"我在找钥匙。","en":"I'm looking for my keys.","r":"Wǒ zài zhǎo yàoshi.","a":"n_07b408f9f20d.mp3"},{"t":"我找不到。","en":"I can't find it.","r":"Wǒ zhǎo bu dào.","a":"n_0a7142f324d7.mp3"},{"t":"我没看到。","en":"I didn't see it.","r":"Wǒ méi kàndào.","a":"n_0ab27803d7fd.mp3"},{"t":"你们有桌位吗？","en":"Do you have a table?","r":"Nǐmen yǒu zhuōwèi ma?","a":"n_5d37cc8456f5.mp3"},{"t":"我想买面包。","en":"I want to buy bread.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng mǎi miànbāo.","a":"n_b7231fef7fb1.mp3"},{"t":"昨天是星期天。","en":"Yesterday was Sunday.","r":"Zuótiān shì xīngqītiān.","a":"n_e6f06e43264b.mp3"},{"t":"你感觉还好吗？","en":"Are you feeling okay?","r":"Nǐ gǎnjué hái hǎo ma?","a":"n_7229fd05a5e7.mp3"},{"t":"你感觉怎么样？","en":"How do you feel?","r":"Nǐ gǎnjué zěnmeyàng?","a":"n_a3c5b1d39619.mp3"},{"t":"我需要吃片药。","en":"I need a pill.","r":"Wǒ xūyào chī piàn yào.","a":"n_9c962edf1eb1.mp3"},{"t":"我是西班牙人。","en":"I'm from Spain.","r":"Wǒ shì Xībānyá rén.","a":"n_6158842ae338.mp3"},{"t":"她很忙。","en":"She's busy.","r":"Tā hěn máng.","a":"n_6a9b9eaff9e2.mp3"},{"t":"我得走了。","en":"I have to go.","r":"Wǒ děi zǒu le.","a":"n_e8843c4636ee.mp3"},{"t":"你生我气了吗？","en":"Are you mad at me?","r":"Nǐ shēng wǒ qì le ma?","a":"n_91bccf665d24.mp3"},{"t":"你能帮我吗？","en":"Can you help me?","r":"Nǐ néng bāng wǒ ma?","a":"n_d71696f1b1cd.mp3"},{"t":"我二十岁。","en":"I'm twenty years old.","r":"Wǒ èrshí suì.","a":"n_272070a36223.mp3"},{"t":"我需要你帮忙。","en":"I need your help.","r":"Wǒ xūyào nǐ bāngmáng.","a":"n_0ef45cf7b333.mp3"},{"t":"我欠你多少钱？","en":"How much do I owe you?","r":"Wǒ qiàn nǐ duōshao qián?","a":"n_446713f67bed.mp3"},{"t":"别太晚回来。","en":"Don't come back late.","r":"Bié tài wǎn huílái.","a":"n_af647bef285c.mp3"},{"t":"你昨天做什么了？","en":"What did you do yesterday?","r":"Nǐ zuótiān zuò shénme le?","a":"n_058bf5d39906.mp3"},{"t":"我们去旅行了。","en":"We took a trip.","r":"Wǒmen qù lǚxíng le.","a":"n_c43eee400c44.mp3"},{"t":"这个我们都知道。","en":"We all know that.","r":"Zhège wǒmen dōu zhīdào.","a":"n_9f46ce36a4c3.mp3"},{"t":"我们不知道。","en":"We don't know.","r":"Wǒmen bù zhīdào.","a":"n_87b0fd49b52d.mp3"},{"t":"你看到那房子了吗？","en":"Do you see the house?","r":"Nǐ kàndào nà fángzi le ma?","a":"n_be499c4322ed.mp3"},{"t":"我给你看看。","en":"I'll show you.","r":"Wǒ gěi nǐ kànkan.","a":"n_bc13b85afdd8.mp3"},{"t":"把手给我。","en":"Give me your hand.","r":"Bǎ shǒu gěi wǒ.","a":"n_3a295dedb383.mp3"},{"t":"尝一点吧。","en":"Try a little.","r":"Cháng yìdiǎn ba.","a":"n_2aa19ed77138.mp3"},{"t":"明天是星期二。","en":"Tomorrow is Tuesday.","r":"Míngtiān shì xīngqī'èr.","a":"n_8aeab5116f9e.mp3"},{"t":"等两分钟。","en":"Wait two minutes.","r":"Děng liǎng fēnzhōng.","a":"n_547843c8ce0c.mp3"},{"t":"它们要二十欧元。","en":"They cost twenty euros.","r":"Tāmen yào èrshí ōuyuán.","a":"n_86b9dda79d9a.mp3"},{"t":"我有两个兄弟。","en":"I have two brothers.","r":"Wǒ yǒu liǎng ge xiōngdì.","a":"n_2ffe329fd5c8.mp3"},{"t":"你得小心点。","en":"You must be careful.","r":"Nǐ děi xiǎoxīn diǎn.","a":"n_47de18d33af4.mp3"},{"t":"他们明天来。","en":"They're coming tomorrow.","r":"Tāmen míngtiān lái.","a":"n_cd59dc7657b3.mp3"},{"t":"我们在做计划。","en":"We're making a plan.","r":"Wǒmen zài zuò jìhuà.","a":"n_39d33c0a8393.mp3"},{"t":"帮我个忙。","en":"Do me a favor.","r":"Bāng wǒ ge máng.","a":"n_7ea2ded315fd.mp3"},{"t":"我想问你点事。","en":"I want to ask you something.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng wèn nǐ diǎn shì.","a":"n_e4e2a83f948a.mp3"},{"t":"我认识玛丽亚。","en":"I know María.","r":"Wǒ rènshi Mǎlìyà.","a":"n_4ecf22a82fd4.mp3"},{"t":"在家里找找。","en":"Look for it at home.","r":"Zài jiā lǐ zhǎozhao.","a":"n_09fd9e64830b.mp3"},{"t":"给我看看照片。","en":"Show me the photo.","r":"Gěi wǒ kànkan zhàopiàn.","a":"n_cd0cf48c6eda.mp3"},{"t":"我在看电视。","en":"I'm watching TV.","r":"Wǒ zài kàn diànshì.","a":"n_cd27e2cfb86c.mp3"},{"t":"给我一分钟。","en":"Give me a minute.","r":"Gěi wǒ yì fēnzhōng.","a":"n_be23308f55d7.mp3"},{"t":"看看谁来了。","en":"Look who's here.","r":"Kànkan shéi lái le.","a":"n_c012c28eadce.mp3"},{"t":"我去洗个澡。","en":"I'm going to take a shower.","r":"Wǒ qù xǐ ge zǎo.","a":"n_e41be27ac4b8.mp3"},{"t":"你睡得很晚吗？","en":"Do you go to bed late?","r":"Nǐ shuì de hěn wǎn ma?","a":"n_7d474ddb0ae0.mp3"},{"t":"你是工作还是上学？","en":"Do you work or study?","r":"Nǐ shì gōngzuò háishi shàngxué?","a":"n_e9f01e737b1f.mp3"},{"t":"我们一起起床。","en":"We get up together.","r":"Wǒmen yìqǐ qǐchuáng.","a":"n_f1e431ff7fe2.mp3"},{"t":"你有什么推荐的？","en":"What do you recommend?","r":"Nǐ yǒu shénme tuījiàn de?","a":"n_21e722dcb6f6.mp3"},{"t":"我讨厌星期一。","en":"I hate Mondays.","r":"Wǒ tǎoyàn xīngqīyī.","a":"n_084d0af51826.mp3"},{"t":"现在是一月。","en":"It's January.","r":"Xiànzài shì yīyuè.","a":"n_a8bfda4d044e.mp3"},{"t":"我付现金。","en":"I'll pay in cash.","r":"Wǒ fù xiànjīn.","a":"n_312ae9a369a4.mp3"},{"t":"今天你请客。","en":"Today you're paying.","r":"Jīntiān nǐ qǐngkè.","a":"n_1dfb2f46e7f2.mp3"},{"t":"我今天不舒服。","en":"I'm sick today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān bù shūfu.","a":"n_4a84d866d3cf.mp3"},{"t":"多喝点水。","en":"Drink lots of water.","r":"Duō hē diǎn shuǐ.","a":"n_ee88549463f6.mp3"},{"t":"给他个机会。","en":"Give him a chance.","r":"Gěi tā ge jīhuì.","a":"n_d2435df413f3.mp3"},{"t":"对，是我。","en":"Yes, that's me.","r":"Duì, shì wǒ.","a":"n_1d5035095822.mp3"},{"t":"对，我看到了。","en":"Yes, I see it.","r":"Duì, wǒ kàndào le.","a":"n_b03999917257.mp3"},{"t":"对，我准备好了。","en":"Yes, I'm ready.","r":"Duì, wǒ zhǔnbèi hǎo le.","a":"n_274364fe4798.mp3"},{"t":"很好，谢谢。","en":"Very well, thanks.","r":"Hěn hǎo, xièxie.","a":"n_a1ebc7082551.mp3"},{"t":"不，我热。","en":"No, I'm hot.","r":"Bù, wǒ rè.","a":"n_8945f1089de5.mp3"},{"t":"不，往那边拐。","en":"No, turn over there.","r":"Bù, wǎng nàbiān guǎi.","a":"n_a892fa3b4bcd.mp3"},{"t":"嗨，我是卡洛斯。","en":"Hi, I'm Carlos.","r":"Hāi, wǒ shì Kǎluòsī.","a":"n_f14bf437388c.mp3"},{"t":"当然，你可以问。","en":"Sure, you can ask.","r":"Dāngrán, nǐ kěyǐ wèn.","a":"n_a587457d1100.mp3"},{"t":"你看，我现在懂了。","en":"Look, now I get it.","r":"Nǐ kàn, wǒ xiànzài dǒng le.","a":"n_9bbd99a0cb70.mp3"},{"t":"不好意思，我迷路了。","en":"Sorry, I'm lost.","r":"Bù hǎoyìsi, wǒ mílù le.","a":"n_9f6cdabf050e.mp3"},{"t":"嗨，最近怎么样？","en":"Hi, how's it going?","r":"Hāi, zuìjìn zěnmeyàng?","a":"n_1815136c0870.mp3"},{"t":"嗯，我想试试。","en":"Yeah, I want to try it.","r":"Èn, wǒ xiǎng shìshi.","a":"n_4f87e3a9aa2c.mp3"},{"t":"你出门的时候跟我说一声。","en":"When you head out, let me know.","r":"Nǐ chūmén de shíhou gēn wǒ shuō yìshēng.","a":"n_9661cf35050f.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道我要什么。","en":"I don't know what I want.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào wǒ yào shénme.","a":"n_4c500dd44cac.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道为什么。","en":"I don't know why.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào wèishénme.","a":"n_81dafd9628d6.mp3"},{"t":"我不在家。","en":"I'm not home.","r":"Wǒ bú zài jiā.","a":"n_3e1611f155cf.mp3"},{"t":"我没那么喜欢。","en":"I don't like it that much.","r":"Wǒ méi nàme xǐhuan.","a":"n_1ab4c0753bf7.mp3"},{"t":"房子在这儿。","en":"The house is here.","r":"Fángzi zài zhèr.","a":"n_1b2f7f2c9b86.mp3"},{"t":"她是本地人。","en":"She's from here.","r":"Tā shì běndì rén.","a":"n_3444214af4f4.mp3"},{"t":"我喜欢咖啡。","en":"I like coffee.","r":"Wǒ xǐhuan kāfēi.","a":"n_56629b8bf0e3.mp3"},{"t":"你喜欢咖啡吗？","en":"Do you like coffee?","r":"Nǐ xǐhuan kāfēi ma?","a":"n_de8b263ee357.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都不知道。","en":"I don't know anything.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu bù zhīdào.","a":"n_2e41ba0e75a3.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都吃不下。","en":"I can't eat anything.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu chī bu xià.","a":"n_5f4d327a45f8.mp3"},{"t":"我去吃点东西。","en":"I'm going to eat something.","r":"Wǒ qù chī diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_f0b373fbd2bd.mp3"},{"t":"我想吃点东西。","en":"I want something to eat.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng chī diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_bcb52f688588.mp3"},{"t":"我现在就去吃。","en":"I'm going to eat now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài jiù qù chī.","a":"n_3e9bc3b2d6a4.mp3"}]}